{
  "name": "Ghost Button",
  "tier": "02_components",
  "key": "ghostButton",
  "type": "atom",
  "description": "",
  "guidelines": {
    "_rawHtml": "\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Guide</h2>\n        <div class=\"guide-card\">\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Purpose</h3>\n            <p>Ghost ButtonはContainerを持たず、視覚的な強調を最小限に抑えたButtonです。主に補助的、または低優先度のアクションに使用され、他のButtonやコンテンツを妨げることなく操作を提供します。</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Anatomy</h3>\n            <ul class=\"guide-list\">\n              <li>Label</li>\n              <li>Left icon（任意）</li>\n              <li>Right icon（任意）</li>\n              <li>Container（スタイル、角丸、サイズ）</li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Priority System</h3>\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\">Primary</h4>\n            <p>Button-Primaryなどの主要なアクションを補助したり、追加の選択肢を提供する場合に使用します。</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-300);margin-top:var(--space-lg);flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--xlarge\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">primary-ghost-button</span></button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--xlarge state-hovered\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">primary-ghost-button</span></button>\n            </div>\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\" style=\"margin-top:var(--spacing-500);\">Secondary</h4>\n            <p>中立的または低優先度の操作（キャンセル、閉じるなど）に使用します。</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-300);margin-top:var(--space-lg);flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--secondary ghost-btn--xlarge\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">secondary-ghost-button</span></button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--secondary ghost-btn--xlarge state-hovered\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">secondary-ghost-button</span></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Style</h3>\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\">Size</h4>\n            <p>利用シーンやレイアウトに応じて高さとパディングが決まります。</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-200);align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:var(--space-lg);\">\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--xlarge\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">xlarge</span></button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">large</span></button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--medium\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">medium</span></button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--small\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">small</span></button>\n            </div>\n\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\" style=\"margin-top:var(--spacing-500);\">State</h4>\n            <p>ユーザーのインタラクション状態を反映した視覚フィードバックとなります。</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--space-xs);align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:var(--space-lg);\">\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-xs);\">\n                <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Label</span></button>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">enabled</span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-xs);\">\n                <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large state-hovered\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Label</span></button>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">hovered</span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-xs);\">\n                <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large state-focused\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Label</span></button>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">focused</span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-xs);\">\n                <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large state-pressed\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Label</span></button>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">pressed</span>\n              </div>\n              <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-xs);\">\n                <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large state-disabled\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Label</span></button>\n                <span style=\"font-size: var(--text-size-xs);;color: var(--color-content-tertiary);\">disabled</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <h4 class=\"guide-sub-heading\" style=\"margin-top:var(--spacing-500);\">Icon Controls</h4>\n            <p>コンテンツ構成に応じてアイコン表示が自動的に制御されます。</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-200);align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:var(--space-lg);\">\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large\">' + STAR_ICON + '<span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Left icon</span></button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">Right icon</span>' + STAR_ICON + '</button>\n              <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--large icon-only\">' + STAR_ICON + '</button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"guide-block\">\n            <h3 class=\"guide-heading\">Do &amp; Don't</h3>\n            <div class=\"do-dont-grid\">\n              <div class=\"do-card\">\n                <div class=\"do-card-header do\">✓ Do</div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-body\" style=\"flex-direction:column;gap:var(--spacing-200);align-items:flex-start;\">\n                  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-200);flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n                    <button class=\"btn btn--xlarge btn--solid-primary\">確認</button>\n                    <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--secondary ghost-btn--xlarge\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">キャンセル</span></button>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-desc\">Button-Primaryと組み合わせ、操作の階層を維持する。ラベルは意図を明確に示す言葉を使用する。</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"do-card\">\n                <div class=\"do-card-header dont\">✕ Don't</div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-body\" style=\"flex-direction:column;gap:var(--spacing-200);align-items:flex-start;opacity:0.6;\">\n                  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-200);flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n                    <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--primary ghost-btn--xlarge\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">確認</span></button>\n                    <button class=\"ghost-btn ghost-btn--secondary ghost-btn--xlarge\"><span class=\"ghost-btn-label\">キャンセル</span></button>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"do-card-desc\">Ghost buttonのみでアクションを誘導しない。最も重要なアクションには必ずButton-Primaryを使用する。</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n    "
  },
  "usage_fn": "DS.ghostButton(opts)"
}